For future reference, PathPlanner offers no suggestions as to how to initialize or tune the PPLTVController. Using trial and error I have settled on the following as being usable, but not great, settings…

double allQ = 0.03; double allR = 0.05; PPLTVController controller = new PPLTVController( VecBuilder.fill(allQ, allQ, allQ), VecBuilder.fill(allR, allR), 0.02);

I also made by own controller with a simple P constant based on pose2d error. That worked well too. I suspect that PPLTVController could work better but not sure how best to do tuning other than trial-and-error, which I already tried.
